display_long_description:
At first, no one believed Mr. Balanger. The owner of a small-town market, he claimed UFOs were hovering over his store. The blurry, poorly taken photos he showed didn’t help his case.

But then things got worse. Objects began disappearing, strange noises echoed at night, and Mr. Balanger swore he saw shadows moving in and out of the building. After countless calls to the police, they finally decided to check it out.

What they found was undeniable. The lights in the sky were real, but now it seemed the aliens had come down. The market was surrounded by strange beings, and the town was in panic.

And who gets called to handle this mess? You—the only ufologist around.

I know you’re scared. But this is your job. Grab your gear, head out there, and deal with these aliens. Mr. Balanger just wants his market back, and it’s up to you to make it happen.
